  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_080a_000174",
    "sentence": "憲府文章之盛，冠於當世。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_005_080a_000175",
    "sentence": "毅早卒，著詩、賦、誄、頌、祝文、《七激》、連珠凡二十八篇。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "《七激》",
        "label": "TITLE",
